name: Where the 5 roads meet (Animation)
description:
The directions were not four but five, i sat down in the middle to think. the answer would be harder than expected!

5 star symmetry is one of my favourites and the colour in this piece is extremely soothing to me.

usually i would be putting this type of work in my kalamint collection however i figured my HEN community might like it.  

for more animations like this visit me on https://kalamint.io/user/witherbloom
